data.description: Offered for sale is this stately lakefront home nestled in the highly-desirable gated community of Neuse Colony! Privately situated on a 1.16 acre lot, this gorgeous home features a heated salt water pool, immediate access to miles of neighborhood trails and golf cart paths, and deeded access to the stocked 4-acre lake which allows for fishing, operating non-motorized boats, and dock installations for waterfront owners! The home features four bedrooms and a bonus room that easily functions as a fifth, four full bathrooms, one half bath, four flex areas, two kitchens, a sun-room that overlooks the pool and lake, formal and non-formal dining, a two-car garage, a walkout basement, a cellar, and storage GALORE! The basement could easily be quartered off to function as a two-bedroom apartment with its own entrance and screened-in porch. Upgrades to this home since 2017 include two new HVAC systems, a new kitchen in the basement, new water filtration system for the pool, new hardwoods throughout the main floor, new deck off the sunroom, a tankless water heater, and two 50-amp outlets installed outside.
